==Korean==

===Interogative pronoun===
'''뭐''' ''mwuh''
(abbreviation of [[무엇]] moo-uht)
# [[what]] - used in questions
#: 이게 '''뭐'''예요? (''Igeh mwuh-yeyo?'') '''What''' is this?
#: '''뭐'''라고 했어요? (''mwuh-rago hessuhyo?'') '''''What''' did [you] say?''

